author: jwaldman
msg: TRINIDAD-1995 typo in base-desktop.css @locales should be @locale
This will change the css for windows,ppc AND IE AND locale ja, zh, ko: AFFieldText and AFFieldTextDisabled will have font-size: 100%.
This will also change the css for windows,ppc AND gecko AND locale th (Thai). .AFDefaultFontFamily:alias will be Browallia and font-size will be 16pt.
This typo was introduced when converted from xss to css in the past 6 months.
